Description: Schaefer cortical atlas for the 'ggseg' ecosystem. Provides
    unified 'ggseg_atlas' objects with both 2D polygon geometry and 3D vertex
    indices, for use with 'ggseg' and 'ggseg3d'. Includes 7-network and
    17-network parcellations at resolutions from 100 to 1000 parcels.
